<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870317-0101 </DOCNO><HL> Financing Business:Loblaw Cos.</HL><DD> 03/17/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> T.LBOND MARKET NEWS (BON) </IN><TEXT>   LOBLAW COS. said it intends to issue $75 million (Canadian) of 10% debentures. The Toronto-based grocery store chain said the Series 8 debentures will be due in 2007. Proceeds will be used for general corporate purposes. Burns Fry Ltd. and McLeod Young Weir Ltd. have agreed to underwrite the issue. </TEXT></DOC>